
ðŸ”Œ Wiring for Wokwi:
LED Color	Arduino Pin
Red	10
Yellow	9
Green	8

Each LED should have a resistor (220Î©) in series with its cathode going to GND.

âœ… Arduino Code (.ino file):
cpp
Copy
Edit
#define RED_LED 10
#define YELLOW_LED 9
#define GREEN_LED 8

void setup() {
  pinMode(RED_LED, OUTPUT);
  pinMode(YELLOW_LED, OUTPUT);
  pinMode(GREEN_LED, OUTPUT);
}

void loop() {
  // Green on - Go
  digitalWrite(GREEN_LED, HIGH);
  digitalWrite(YELLOW_LED, LOW);
  digitalWrite(RED_LED, LOW);
  delay(5000); // Green for 5 seconds

  // Yellow on - Prepare to stop
  digitalWrite(GREEN_LED, LOW);
  digitalWrite(YELLOW_LED, HIGH);
  delay(2000); // Yellow for 2 seconds

  // Red on - Stop
  digitalWrite(YELLOW_LED, LOW);
  digitalWrite(RED_LED, HIGH);
  delay(5000); // Red for 5 seconds
}
